function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

	err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.0.249!');
}

	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (is_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.png') && (sha1_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.png') != '6e3963b0b3ffc910241852ee2aeab67fd9a1a83d')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/class_diagram.png');
	$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/class_diagram.png');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/class_diagram.png')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('includes/classes/class_diagram.png', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_7();
if (!is_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.png')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/class_diagram.png');
} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/class_diagram.png') != '6e3963b0b3ffc910241852ee2aeab67fd9a1a83d') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/class_diagram.png');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/class_diagram.png', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/class_diagram.png');
}

// Dir added: setup/doc
@mkdir('setup/doc');
if (!is_dir('setup/doc')) {
	warn('Directory could not be created: setup/doc');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/doc', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change directory permissions of setup/doc');
}

if (is_file('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') && (sha1_file('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') != '34424f058b2622135c0f9b55c0dda420d54d1b90')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_8();
if (!is_file('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
} else if (sha1_file('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') != '34424f058b2622135c0f9b55c0dda420d54d1b90') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
}

if (is_file('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') && (sha1_file('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') != '7027b1cde97a0557df13f6c5919ca76cd250ae22')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
	$tmp = pathinfo('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_9();
if (!is_file('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
} else if (sha1_file('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') != '7027b1cde97a0557df13f6c5919ca76cd250ae22') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
}

if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: ajax.php');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('ajax.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): ajax.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('ajax.php') != '1e1efd168a95ff69fc5a8c5cdc338c53ed1f66b9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('ajax.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of ajax.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '1e1efd168a95ff69fc5a8c5cdc338c53ed1f66b9') {
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '7932dedd7db741694b0480c834275f7ce7e19173') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: ajax.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('ajax.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('ajax.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('ajax.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('ajax.php') !== '1e1efd168a95ff69fc5a8c5cdc338c53ed1f66b9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != '5d04c9a56aee711a90efd4cefd78cd54d893220b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '5d04c9a56aee711a90efd4cefd78cd54d893220b') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '45fd2e34938c3af4f9ab80ba1a763df793aadbad') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '5d04c9a56aee711a90efd4cefd78cd54d893220b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php');
	writefile_14();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php') != 'ca01606570058106b877159c89e88cef0abc70c9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php') !== 'ca01606570058106b877159c89e88cef0abc70c9') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php') !== '1e23c75b4cb13edc27289679586a789bb9df979a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php') !== 'ca01606570058106b877159c89e88cef0abc70c9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabasePlugin.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	writefile_25();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') != 'e5903a051293f0f0167138822765fc5253c3a6b8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidplus.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== 'e5903a051293f0f0167138822765fc5253c3a6b8') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== '1f08d6f5082179541ca7abf16111c8636f52f3d2') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidplus.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidplus.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidplus.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidplus.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_25();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== 'e5903a051293f0f0167138822765fc5253c3a6b8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/xml_utils.inc.php');
	writefile_26();
	if (!is_file('includes/xml_utils.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/xml_utils.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/xml_utils.inc.php') != '0acebfde037341bfcdef09602e4e3956afb75411') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/xml_utils.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/xml_utils.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/xml_utils.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/xml_utils.inc.php') !== '0acebfde037341bfcdef09602e4e3956afb75411') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/xml_utils.inc.php') !== '44d9478da095bc67b90a51400b969d86f98b0a96') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/xml_utils.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/xml_utils.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/xml_utils.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/xml_utils.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_26();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/xml_utils.inc.php') !== '0acebfde037341bfcdef09602e4e3956afb75411') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/xml_utils.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_29();
	if (!is_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php') != 'b58a92e810487d5bd48f26f8c6da3d45d0083701') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php') !== 'b58a92e810487d5bd48f26f8c6da3d45d0083701') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php') !== '83c15651bde5ac6ec91a7977e17c8c6c017bf92c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_29();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php') !== 'b58a92e810487d5bd48f26f8c6da3d45d0083701') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/110_system_config/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/130_create_ra/plugin.inc.php') !== '8ccc509109d4971d0a3e381f9e6a2218d5697436') {

		}
	}
}

	writefile_35();
	if (!is_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php') != '26419e6ddfaf794d78aade554704a04a236333a3') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php') !== '26419e6ddfaf794d78aade554704a04a236333a3') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php') !== 'df0905661f80fe64299a23d7d5d2b65b5659a21e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_35();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php') !== '26419e6ddfaf794d78aade554704a04a236333a3') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/700_colors/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_37();
	if (!is_file('plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php') != '9c7c77285627652e2bd3d3a416953a663fd83978') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php') !== '9c7c77285627652e2bd3d3a416953a663fd83978') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php') !== '08e82b228b138bff13eaf9659a25f360d51802af') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php');

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_37();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php') !== '9c7c77285627652e2bd3d3a416953a663fd83978') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/900_software_update/plugin.inc.php');
		}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_38();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') != 'edb3adfb6787bf15dfa8a464d33e76d71808be6e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') !== 'edb3adfb6787bf15dfa8a464d33e76d71808be6e') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') !== 'b90d1ba50e700970243f84b2a8cde5fa86f1423b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_38();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php') !== 'edb3adfb6787bf15dfa8a464d33e76d71808be6e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/mysqli/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_39();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php') != '63729d92c06fd2cd6ebb9b0929075b784b054196') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php') !== '63729d92c06fd2cd6ebb9b0929075b784b054196') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php') !== 'ba2e66314103dbf90d1e22fae7de873df29d46b7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_39();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php') !== '63729d92c06fd2cd6ebb9b0929075b784b054196') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/odbc/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_40();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php') != '631f30329e8829930a89e792983f692b2ddd6164') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php') !== '631f30329e8829930a89e792983f692b2ddd6164') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php') !== '8c253315a549abc392c78522a85c63d5634e27ad') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_40();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php') !== '631f30329e8829930a89e792983f692b2ddd6164') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pdo/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_41();
	if (!is_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php') != 'b7d32df9aa18234fb3ecddeabc7d283feb4fedcc') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php') !== 'b7d32df9aa18234fb3ecddeabc7d283feb4fedcc') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php') !== '63e5f8add607e8c0d299b2632ff25f8156ed24ba') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_41();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php') !== 'b7d32df9aa18234fb3ecddeabc7d283feb4fedcc') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/doi/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

				warn('Creation of backup failed');

	}

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php') !== '5f1d919585b9392901ba875ee7fe6cc437c2d330') {

			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/java/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {

		writefile_45();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') != 'f521abe537c5ffca132093c2ebe488c7a1b5174b') {

		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') !== 'f521abe537c5ffca132093c2ebe488c7a1b5174b') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') !== '181f0537ff2bbadbc6fa92b56e5ad1bbd352cdb1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php');

			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_46();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php') !== 'f521abe537c5ffca132093c2ebe488c7a1b5174b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/oid/plugin.inc.php');

if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_48();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') != '40159fd2fc6f79a4a604419bef7cb5d8d42bfe3d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== '40159fd2fc6f79a4a604419bef7cb5d8d42bfe3d') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== '4fb0895d75af9f14001d516c109ae52d571584dc') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_48();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php') !== '40159fd2fc6f79a4a604419bef7cb5d8d42bfe3d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/090_login/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_49();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php') != '14e46a8854e3b76f24ce459a15412f5e15b79a43') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php') !== '14e46a8854e3b76f24ce459a15412f5e15b79a43') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php') !== 'eb639c750a25132553c9160ab9bb7feac7ad8751') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_49();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php') !== '14e46a8854e3b76f24ce459a15412f5e15b79a43') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/091_forgot_password/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_51();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php') !== 'fa4f0ec34467948314e43c10e952d82303951dc5') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php') != '59a3a02cc152d483b0aeaa5e62467f1579bc86bd') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php') !== '59a3a02cc152d483b0aeaa5e62467f1579bc86bd') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php') !== '7143cdf08355480d75c11256598c9ee63ed8cb01') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_53();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php') !== '59a3a02cc152d483b0aeaa5e62467f1579bc86bd') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/300_search/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_54();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php') != 'd74dccd10ddc3fc1d1c5c88dc2dcb98b77560e07') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php') !== 'd74dccd10ddc3fc1d1c5c88dc2dcb98b77560e07') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php') !== '411ae86679c047aff43fa3c2cd999b386f5f9934') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_54();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php') !== 'd74dccd10ddc3fc1d1c5c88dc2dcb98b77560e07') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/500_resources/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_55();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/raPages/092_invite/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/raPages/092_invite/plugin.inc.php') != '8048c88a612aeda2c95b36c5c6938d3e858fb742') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/092_invite/plugin.inc.php');

	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/092_invite/plugin.inc.php') !== '8048c88a612aeda2c95b36c5c6938d3e858fb742') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/092_invite/plugin.inc.php') !== '193d9b5d9134af6150724428ee0e8b2cb27e2017') {

				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/092_invite/plugin.inc.php') !== '8048c88a612aeda2c95b36c5c6938d3e858fb742') {

if (!is_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_56();
	if (!is_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php') != 'f77dae559757aee822b3f5fb949de90beeb52a0c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php') !== 'f77dae559757aee822b3f5fb949de90beeb52a0c') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php') !== 'f1c2c69a958ef6c6371bea4e4102dc7491b39e79') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_56();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php') !== 'f77dae559757aee822b3f5fb949de90beeb52a0c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/100_edit_contact_data/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_57();
	if (!is_file('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php') != 'c730d2975e7498b3e7dfbae2b4032587c1adc95d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php') !== 'c730d2975e7498b3e7dfbae2b4032587c1adc95d') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php') !== '2ae352394a2e2b29fb2274a7aa2788efa6e4ea6a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_57();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php') !== 'c730d2975e7498b3e7dfbae2b4032587c1adc95d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/101_change_password/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php') != 'd879b619126b4b2215eb9c207e13f4f2df85ad4b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php') !== 'd879b619126b4b2215eb9c207e13f4f2df85ad4b') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php') !== 'a89c8e2bd8d99e88b1ae752abf6e0eb3589bc925') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_58();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php') !== 'd879b619126b4b2215eb9c207e13f4f2df85ad4b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/102_change_email/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php');
	writefile_59();
	if (!is_file('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php') != '0886b3a82d1155475272d6782bd54a63c0400805') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php') !== '0886b3a82d1155475272d6782bd54a63c0400805') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php') !== '81b0c0adb7d1e36951ae56dd9fd5ef10235cf858') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_59();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php') !== '0886b3a82d1155475272d6782bd54a63c0400805') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/raPages/200_log/plugin.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/index.php');
	writefile_60();
	if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/index.php') != 'a9db3245ce553af5d3e1ca5f13c77042d6907864') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== 'a9db3245ce553af5d3e1ca5f13c77042d6907864') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== '20a1f40eb8620e110757252eb91f434b22787729') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_60();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== 'a9db3245ce553af5d3e1ca5f13c77042d6907864') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php');
	writefile_61();
	if (!is_file('update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php') != 'e1bded0f76ea8ee4117dfd654ef8c97e06445063') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php') !== 'e1bded0f76ea8ee4117dfd654ef8c97e06445063') {
		if (@sha1_file('update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php') !== 'a57377158f62d270077c38684b81ed7fa9ec7bc3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_61();
		if (@sha1_file('update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php') !== 'e1bded0f76ea8ee4117dfd654ef8c97e06445063') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): update/includes/phpsvnclient.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('update/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: update/index.php');
	writefile_62();
	if (!is_file('update/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): update/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('update/index.php') != 'cc697ec6ecfb6ccda3555479b477755c0de6bad1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): update/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('update/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of update/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== 'cc697ec6ecfb6ccda3555479b477755c0de6bad1') {
		if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== '5d95d5e440083a2e3a1f07d52cde8f8d01e75c9b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: update/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('update/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('update/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('update/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_62();
		if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== 'cc697ec6ecfb6ccda3555479b477755c0de6bad1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): update/index.php');
		}
	}
}

// File deleted: includes/SecureMailer.class.php
@unlink('includes/SecureMailer.class.php');
if (is_file('includes/SecureMailer.class.php')) {
	warn('File could not be deleted: includes/SecureMailer.class.php');
}

// File deleted: includes/classes/OIDplusTree.class.php
@unlink('includes/classes/OIDplusTree.class.php');
if (is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusTree.class.php')) {
	warn('File could not be deleted: includes/classes/OIDplusTree.class.php');
}


file_put_contents('oidplus_version.txt', "Revision 250\n");
if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 250') err('Could not write to oidplus_version.txt!');


echo 'DONE'; // This exact string will be compared in Update v3

@unlink(__FILE__);
if (is_file(__FILE__)) warn('Could not delete '.basename(__FILE__).'! Please delete it manually');
